				<td colspan="2"><span>Could anyone explain to me a little more about swarm kiting? I am a 52 bard of the Nameless, and the only AoE songs i have are point blank? Is there some song that I am missing? I would much appreciate the education of swarm kiting <img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-2.gif" border="0" alt="Big Smile" hspace="2" /> </span></td>
