				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Swarm Kiting<a name="72049"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Jan 11 05 6:32 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Plenty in the guides section on swarm kiting, you could also call it charmkiting if you like. AoE songs have nothing to do with it. That is AE kiting and no longer available to bards.
<br />
In a nutshell, grab a bunch of mobs, charm one, send it against the rest, break charm before your pet dies, and kill it yourself. Rinse and repeat.</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
