			<tr>
				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Swarm Kiting<a name="72084"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Jan 12 05 12:17 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>As a Bard thats been doing PoN Dogs since 51 heres what you'll need to do. First follow the song list described by first reply BUT drop the Cantata song and replace with your snare/slow song. From there place your drum in primary and put your wind instrument in your inventory slot where a bag would go for easy access. Make sure to have a wind instrument that can be put into primary slot. If you dont have one, one can be bought in bazaar for under 100pp.
<br />

<br />
From there youll start near the dead tree by the hill. (also if you have the expansion place some points in tribute and get flowing thought tribute for mana regen or else you will more then likely go oom. With FT 4 from tribute im never less then 80% mana and only costs 29 points per 10 mins) 
<br />

<br />
Now charm the first dog near the hill thats alone and send him after a dog in the far back corner to agro the camp. At this point make sure to have selos chorus up and now switch to wind instrument. You  can target to your pet at any time by just hitting F1 twice. It toggles yourself then pet. When pet gets down to 25% start invis song, you'll invis and your pet will usually be between 5-10% health. Now reequip your drum and play selos fast. Now run a few circles to get them tight and proceed to use your 4 chants to chant down your old pet till dead.  (You gain experience)
<br />

<br />
Once your initial pet is dead run a few secs away from group, turn and target next dog. From here refresh selos fast then use charm. Make sure to watch for the charm resist message. If you get a resist dont switch targets and retry because youll build agro and the mobs wont agro your pet. Now if you successfully charmed pet then turn again and sick pet on next mob. From there watch to see if any chase you after you send pet. You want to tap F1 twice to retarget pet and now reequip wind instrument. Watch pets health and again wait till 25% then start invis song. Once charm is broke reequip drum, refresh selos and proceed to chant down. 
<br />

<br />
Rinse repeat... till your down to last mob. Now once your down to the last one just chant it down to 20% health. Once it hits 20% itll want to run and this is where you snare mob and melee it down rest of way. 
<br />

<br />
Now theres an outline of trees near the clearing of dog camp. You want to make sure you and your mobs never go past that line of trees or else your going to agro more trees and spiders then you can count and you cant charm those. For advanced kiters you can use the dogs to tank these down if you like. Otherwise just zone and try again. 
<br />

<br />
Any questions?
<br />

<br />

<br />
</span></td>
